entries.som_kenobi_final_chamber_entrance_item_d: You are not sure what this large pillar is made of but it has a cold aura exuding from it. You get an uneasy feeling of danger, like it's trying to tell you to stay away.

entries.som_kenobi_final_force_crystal_d: The crystal seems charged with some sort of power. As you get closer to it, you swear you can hear horrific screams of pain inside your head. The feeling is overwhelming and almost unbearable.
entries.som_kenobi_fusion_machine_d: Looking at the instructions mounted on the side of this machinery, it seems to be used to fuse together things that normally wouldn't be possible. Rocks, crystals, ore etc.
entries.som_kenobi_hidden_treasure_plaque_d: A tablet with some old inscriptions on it. It's half buried in the lava rock.
entries.som_kenobi_historian_corpse_d: The remains of a long dead humanoid.
entries.som_kenobi_historian_data_disk_2_d: The crystal powered by my fellow Knights is functioning just as intended. The Sith are all but powerless, and victory is within our grasp. I'm concerned about the cracks that we have spotted in the crystal's structure, though...
entries.som_kenobi_historian_data_disk_d: The enemy is at our very gates. My men have fought valiantly alongside the Jedi, but our losses are terrible. The Jedi claim they have a plan to turn the tide, but I don't know if I can trust them. -Major Fewn Hew
